data.description: Welcome to your new home at 1608 16th Ln, #B, Greenacres, FL 33463! This spacious townhouse boasts 3 beds, 3 baths, and 1,488 sq ft of modern living space. The first floor offers a full bed and bath, while upstairs, the master suite features a large walk-in closet and dual vanity. Enjoy outdoor living with a covered patio and open balcony. Plus, community amenities include a clubhouse, pool, tennis courts, and playground. With a 2021 roof and a pet-friendly atmosphere, this home is move-in ready! Schedule your showing today!
